00:29:31.160 --> 00:29:32.200
Oh, no!

596
00:29:32.620 --> 00:29:35.210
Morris' teakwood deck!

597
00:29:35.380 --> 00:29:36.920
Yeah. Grand adventure. Great.

598
00:29:37.090 --> 00:29:38.710
Nice work, Tom Jones.

