00:37:05.530 --> 00:37:06.700
Right.

741
00:37:08.790 --> 00:37:10.620
Yes we are, Cristy.

742
00:37:11.410 --> 00:37:13.170
It's very serious.

743
00:37:13.830 --> 00:37:15.330
It's priority.

744
00:37:15.500 --> 00:37:16.840
Yes it is.

745
00:37:16.920 --> 00:37:17.840
And I'm helping.

746
00:37:17.920 --> 00:37:19.590
Yes you are.

