-Yeah. Come on.

1744
01:34:52.460 --> 01:34:53.830
-I'm not trespassing.
-Yeah, you're trespassing.

1745
01:34:54.000 --> 01:34:55.000
I was in his office.

1746
01:34:55.170 --> 01:34:56.540
-You don't know. Come on.
-He let me into his...

1747
01:34:56.710 --> 01:34:58.090
Gerhardt, you're not gonna
